  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Grand Pas is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner served in the hotel restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental buffet with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner includes 3 courses starter, main and dessert with a choice of 2 options for each dish. Snacks are available from the bar throughout the day at a local charge.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Add on the pre-bookable Ski Inclusive which includes lift pass, skis and boots and 6 vouchers for lunch (sandwich, crisps and a drink) at participating mountain restaurants.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Grand Pas is a very popular choice <span>surrounded by mountains, pristine nature, and is conveniently situated a mere 50 meters away from the Pyrenees' largest ski resort, Grandvalira.</span> Its many leisure facilities make it an excellent choice for families and skiers looking for a quality hotel practically on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Cosy rooms</h2>
<p><span>The contemporary décor and state-of-the-art amenities will ensure your comfort from the moment you arrive. Plus, some of the rooms offer breath-taking mountain views, adding an extra touch to your stay.</span></p>
<h2><span>Rest and relax</span></h2>
<p><span>Whether you choose to unwind in the indoor heated pool, soak in the soothing jacuzzi, or bask in the comforting warmth of the sauna, you'll find the perfect way to relax after a day up in the mountains.  You'll also find a dedicated children's area to entertain the little ones, and a cosy bar where you can savour a refreshing drink to cap off your day.</span></p>
<h2><span>Ideal location</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel is in a prime location close to the slopes. Situated in the centre of Pas de la Casa, you'll discover a range of sports shops, jewellery boutiques, bars and restaurants on your doorstep. And if you're eager to kickstart your sports adventure right away, you'll be delighted to know that the Grandvalira ski area is just a few steps away.</span></p>]]></description>
