  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Grand Pas is virtually ski in/ski out, with the hotel just a 50 metre walk from the ski slopes. Then it's a quick ski down to the ski lifts and ski school meeting place.</p>
<p>It's a 3 minutes' walk (250 metres) uphill from the village centre and the ski hire shop just 2 minutes' walk away (200 metres).</p>]]></locationDescription>
